OL,3,CWhere can you see the Northern Lights
OL,4,Ctonight?
OL,6,FBy ITV News Producer
OL,8,FThe Northern Lights dazzled huge
OL,9,Fswaths of the UK overnight thanks to
OL,10,Fan "extreme" geomagnetic storm.
OL,12,FThe Aurora Borealis was best visible
OL,13,Fin Whitley Bay on the north east
OL,14,Fcoast, Essex, Cambridgeshire and
OL,15,FWokingham in Berkshire.
OL,17,FIt was also spotted in Suffolk, Kent,
OL,18,FHampshire and Liverpool, and was even
OL,19,Fvisible in parts of London.
