OL,3,CWhere can you see the Northern Lights
OL,4,Ctonight?
OL,6,FSo can you spot them tonight if you
OL,7,Fmissed out on Friday?
OL,9,FWhere can you see the Northern Lights
OL,10,Ftonight?
OL,12,FITV News meteorologist and weather
OL,13,Fpresenter Chris Page said it is
OL,14,Fpossible the Northern Lights will be
OL,15,Fvisible this evening.
OL,17,F"Activity is expected to slowly
OL,18,Fdecline, however there is a good
OL,19,Fchance (cloud permitting) you'll be
OL,20,Fable to see it again tonight," he said.
