OL,3,CWhere can you see the Northern Lights
OL,4,Ctonight?
OL,6,FChris Snell, a meteorologist at the
OL,7,FMet Office, said there were sightings
OL,8,Fon Friday night "from top to tail
OL,9,Facross the country".
OL,11,F"It is hard to fully predict what will
OL,12,Fhappen in the Earth's atmosphere, but
OL,13,Fthere will still be enhanced solar
OL,14,Factivity tonight, so the lights could
OL,15,Fbe visible again in northern parts of
OL,16,Fthe UK, including Scotland, Northern
OL,17,FIreland and the far north of England."
