OL,3,CWhere can you see the Northern Lights
OL,4,Ctonight?
OL,6,FMr Snell said there were sightings in
OL,7,Fparts of Europe on Friday night as
OL,8,Fwell, with the Met Office receiving
OL,9,Fpictures and information from
OL,10,Flocations including Prague and
OL,11,FBarcelona.
OL,13,FSightings in southern parts of the UK
OL,14,Fare less likely on Saturday, although
OL,15,FMr Snell said the lights might be
OL,16,Fvisible through a strong camera lens.
