OL,3,CWhere can you see the Northern Lights
OL,4,Ctonight?
OL,6,FWhile short nights limit the
OL,7,Fvisibility window, there's a "good
OL,8,Fchance" of sightings on Saturday
OL,9,Fnight, especially across Scotland,
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland and parts of northern
OL,11,FEngland and Wales, a Met Office
OL,12,Fspokesperson told ITV News.
OL,14,F"There could be some visibility
OL,15,Ffurther south, especially with long-
OL,16,Fexposure cameras."
OL,18,FThe best time to spot the Northern
OL,19,FLights tends to be between 10pm and
OL,20,F2am.
