OL,3,CWhere can you see the Northern Lights
OL,4,Ctonight?
OL,6,FVisibility of the Aurora Borealis will
OL,7,Fcontinue into Sunday night, but cloud
OL,8,Facross the UK, particularly in the
OL,9,FWest, is likely to obscure the view.
OL,11,FAreas in the East have the best chance
OL,12,Fat spotting the colourful skies again
OL,13,Fon Sunday, the Met Office said.
