OL,3,CWhere can you see the Northern Lights
OL,4,Ctonight?
OL,6,FIt's rare that the Northern Lights are
OL,7,Fthis visible in the UK.
OL,9,FFriday night's display has been
OL,10,Fclassified as a G5 Extreme Solar Storm
OL,11,Fby the National Oceanic and
OL,12,FAtmospheric Administration.
OL,14,FThis last happened in October 2003.
OL,16,FWhat's the science behind the Northern
OL,17,FLights?
