OL,3,CWhere can you see the Northern Lights
OL,4,Ctonight?
OL,6,FGreens appear due to interactions with
OL,7,Foxygen, red is from oxygen in the
OL,8,Fupper atmosphere while blues and
OL,9,Fpurples are due to the interaction of
OL,10,Fnitrogen.
